      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S represents the pinnacle of the naturally aspirated flat-six era, featuring the 3.8L 9A1 engine with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) and a robust integrated dry-sump system. Meticulously maintained, the chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, complemented by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a precise six-speed manual transaxle. The exterior boasts original paint with zero rock chips, while the undercarriage remains concours-level clean, showing no signs of heat cycling or fluid seepage. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example with a documented service history and a flawless DME overrev report.",
